data.description: County living with Wal-Mart delivery availability!! Located in Farmington Estates in the highly desired Central Heights Community. This 1,620 sq ft home features 3 BR, 2 BA, attached 2 car garage, safe room (built per FEMA specs), screened back porch, fenced yard and detached shop with garage door. Recently updated with new flooring & fresh paint throughout. New roof in 2022 with added insulation in attic, new gutters, sidewalk, & landscaping. All kitchen appliances remain. The home has closets and cabinets galore. Water heater & HVAC installed in 2014 (unit has been serviced annually).  Buyer to verify all information. Seller is Realtor related. Call now to schedule your private showing!
